data.description: Bring all your toys, as this home boasts an insulated and HEATED 30X30 shop as well as a 3 car garage and is located in the coveted Elder Grove school district! Excellent House for the Price!! Impressive westend home nicely situated on almost 1/2 acre in Linlee lakes Estates Subdivision. 5 bed, 3 bath, living room and family room, recent updates of a pantry and opened kitchen/dining area with coffee nook. Nice master suite which includes a walk-in closet and bath. 2 bedrooms and an additional full bath complete this spacious main level. The downstairs includes 2 large bedrooms, a bathroom, and over-sized laundry/utility room. It has a bar/exercise area and stunning gas fireplace! A beautifully landscaped lawn surrounds a Gazebo and newer hot tub. Wells in the area are built one per 2 homes and maintained by the current $80/MNTH.
